:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 15 Dec 2014 09:20:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=704560\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:373:\"Globe is a WordPress theme able to meet the needs of those willing to make an e-commerce website or simply a corporate.\r\nBuilt on the Yithemes 2.0 framework, Globe has many possible functions and it is easy to use.\r\nSliders, customised 100+ shortcodes, Pre-Launch, Visual Composer and a support team always ready to offer you the help you need. Globe has really everything.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"nando\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21800:\"	<div  class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_tabs wpb_content_element\" data-interval=\"0\">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper wpb_tour_tabs_wrapper ui-tabs vc_clearfix\">\n			<ul class=\"wpb_tabs_nav ui-tabs-nav vc_clearfix\"><li><a href=\"#tab-76a53dbf-e2b6-2\">Main overview</a></li><li><a href=\"#tab-1431599357401-2-2\">Free vs Premium</a></li><li><a href=\"#tab-1427367413392-1-10\">Reviews</a></li></ul>\n\n			\n			<div id=\"tab-76a53dbf-e2b6-2\" class=\"wpb_tab ui-tabs-panel wpb_ui-tabs-hide vc_clearfix\">\n				\n        <div class=\"row product-features\">\n\n            <div class=\"premium-features col-sm-9\">\n                <h3>Premium Features</h3>\n                <ul class=\"list-inline\">\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Support</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/free-support.png\" alt=\"Support\"/>\n                            <p>We offer a year of support with the purchase of the premium version\r\n, so you can open a new ticket and ask help to our developers. </p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Videotutorial</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/videotutorial.png\" alt=\"Videotutorial\"/>\n                            <p>Setting the theme is easier with our videotutorials, so you can watch how to set each page of the theme step by step.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Sample data</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sample-data.png\" alt=\"Sample data\"/>\n                            <p>With a simple click you can import our demo files, so your theme will appear exactly like the theme preview.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Extensive Theme Options</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/theme-options.png\" alt=\"Extensive Theme Options\"/>\n                            <p>With our advanced theme options page, you are given complete control over your theme and its settings. </p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Unlimited colors</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/google-font.png\" alt=\"Unlimited colors\"/>\n                            <p>In the premium version of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links, slogan and so on.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Custom widgets</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/custom-widgets.png\" alt=\"Custom widgets\"/>\n                            <p>Add new and useful widgets in your website pages.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Shortcode manager</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/shortcode-manager.png\" alt=\"Shortcode manager\"/>\n                            <p>Through a simple button in the editor bar, you can easily add shortcode in your posts and pages.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Visual Composer</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/viasual-composer.png\" alt=\"Visual Composer\"/>\n                            <p>This plugin helps the user in the construction of the pages giving you the ability to drag and drop content is backend that frontend, thus providing a preview of the result obtained</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>300+ Shortcode</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/shortcodes.png\" alt=\"300+ Shortcode\"/>\n                            <p>300+ shortcodes to compose your pages and add contents in an easy and rapid way.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Custom Login</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/custom-logo.png\" alt=\"Custom Login\"/>\n                            <p>Choose the colors, the background and the features suitable for your login page</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>backup and reset</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/backup-reset.png\" alt=\"backup and reset\"/>\n                            <p>Import and export the sample data for your theme</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>4 slider types</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/slider-type.png\" alt=\"4 slider types\"/>\n                            <p>Compose your page chosing your favourite slider to display your product and images.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>pre-launch</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/lauch.png\" alt=\"pre-launch\"/>\n                            <p>If your site is under maintenance or in the pre-launch phase, with this plugin you can show to your users a fully customizable page that can include also a countdown.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Zoom product image</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/zoom.png\" alt=\"Zoom product image\"/>\n                            <p>You can add a zoom feature in the featured image of products, on the product detail page.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Wishlist</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/wishlist.png\" alt=\"Wishlist\"/>\n                            <p>Give to users the ability to add the products in own withlist.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                    </ul>\n            </div>\n            <aside class=\"col-sm-3 general-features\">\n\n                <div class=\"quick-info\">\n\n\n                    <h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled info\">\n                        <li>\n                            <span>version <b>1.1.2</b> - released <b>04-27-2015</b></span>\n                        </li>\n\n                    </ul>\n\n\n                    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"http://docs.yithemes.com/globe/\"\n                       title=\"View documentation\"\n                       target=\"_blank\">View documentation</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"#\" title=\"View changelog\"\n                       data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#changelog\">View changelog</a>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"changelog\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-labelledby=\"changelogLabel\"\n                     aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                    <div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n                        <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                            <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                                <button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">&times;</span></button>\n                                \n\n<h2>Version 1.1.2 - Released on Apr 27, 2015</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Added: Wordpress 4.2 compatibility</li>\n        <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.8 support</li>\n        <li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.9</li>\n        <li>Fixed: Wp security issue</li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Version 1.1.1 - Released on Apr 16, 2015</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.7 support</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviewv\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Pdf Invoice</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Cart Message</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Stripe</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Authorize.net</li>\n		<li>Added: YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder</li>\n		<li>Fixed: Rich Snippet</li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Version 1.1.0 - Released on Feb 19, 2015</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Added: Wordpress 4.1.1 support</li>\n        <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.3.4 support</li>\n        <li>Added: Ultimate Addons for Visual Composer 3.9.3</li>\n        <li>Added: Yith Woocommerce Wishlist 2.0</li>\n        <li>Updated: Core framework</li>\n    </ul>\n <h2>Version 1.0.2 - Released on Feb 04, 2015</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Fixed: Issue with woocommerce plugins options</li>\n    </ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 - Released on Feb 02, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.11 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Visual Composer 4.4.2 support</li>\n	<li>Added: Ultimate Addons for Visual Composer 3.9.1</li>\n	<li>Added: Revolution Slider 4.6.5 support</li>\n	<li>Updated: Core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                                    <h3>General features</h3>\n\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled general\">\n                                                    <li>\n                                WP 4.1 Compatible                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Widget ready sidebars                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Valid XHTML / CSS                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Responsive design                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Blog structure + threaded comments                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                IE9+, Firefox, Chrome, Opera and Safari compatible                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Seo optimized                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                WooCommerce 2.3.X Compatible                            </li>\n                                            </ul>\n                \n            </aside>\n\n        </div>\n    	<div  class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\">\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center\">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			<h2 class=\"wpb_heading wpb_singleimage_heading\">Fully responsive design<small>the globe is 100% mobile ready</small></h2>\n			<div class=\"vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"460\" src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/01.jpg\" class=\"vc_single_image-img attachment-large\" alt=\"responsive\" /></div>\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center\">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			<h2 class=\"wpb_headi