o on)</li>\n<li>Services page</li>\n<li>Testimonials page</li>\n<li>Blog (big image style)</li>\n<li>2 Custom widget: testimonials and contact info</li>\n<li>Megamenu support</li>\n<li>Translation ready &amp; WPML compatible</li>\n</ul>\n\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			<h3>PREMIUM VERSION FEATURES</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>All features of the free version</li>\n<li><strong>Premium Revolution Slider included (value 18$)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Visual composer included (value 33$)</strong></li>\n<li>Parallax slider</li>\n<li>About/team page</li>\n<li>Contact page with customizable contact form</li>\n<li><strong>Filterable Faq page</strong></li>\n<li>Prelaunch page with counter</li>\n<li>Custom popup plugin included</li>\n<li><strong>300+ advanced shortcodes</strong></li>\n<li>Advanced shop shortcodes: product sliders, tabs, etc.</li>\n<li>Megamenu support</li>\n<li><strong>Vertical megamenu with images support</strong></li>\n<li>Child theme ready</li>\n<li>Advanced theme options panel to customize typography, colors and other settings</li>\n<li><strong>Support &amp; videotutorials</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Demo files</strong> to easily import our live preview settings in few click</li>\n</ul>\n\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n</div>\n			</div> \n			<div id=\"tab-1427367413392-1-10\" class=\"wpb_tab ui-tabs-panel wpb_ui-tabs-hide vc_clearfix\">\n				\n\n		\n			<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab-reviews\">\n							</div>\n\n		\n\n			</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n</div><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_no_bg\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-v