61.jpg\" class=\"vc_single_image-img attachment-full\" alt=\"WPML\" /></div>\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n</div>\n			</div> \n			<div id=\"tab-1431602192387-2-9\" class=\"wpb_tab ui-tabs-panel wpb_ui-tabs-hide vc_clearfix\">\n					<div  class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\">\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			<h3>FREE VERSION FEATURES</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Static header image</li>\n<li>WooCommerce support to manage your shop</li>\n<li>Wishlist, Compare products &amp; Share products</li>\n<li>Advanced ajax filters in shop page (filter by size, color, price and so on)</li>\n<li>Services page</li>\n<li>Blog (big image style)</li>\n<li>2 Custom widget: testimonials and contact info</li>\n<li>Megamenu support</li>\n<li>Translation ready &amp; WPML compatible</li>\n</ul>\n\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-6 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			<h3>PREMIUM VERSION FEATURES</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>All features of the free version</li>\n<li>3 sliders: Rotating slider, Elastic slider and Flexi slider</li>\n<li>Contact page with customizable contact form</li>\n<li><strong>Filterable Faq page</strong></li>\n<li>Customizable Error 404 page</li>\n<li>Alternative blog layout: small image</li>\n<li><strong>300+ advanced shortcodes</strong></li>\n<li>Advanced shop shortcodes: product sliders, tabs, etc.</li>\n<li>Child theme ready</li>\n<li>Advanced theme options panel to customize typography, colors and other settings</li>\n<li><strong>Support &amp; videotutorials</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Demo files</strong> to easily import our live preview settings in few click</li>\n</ul>\n\n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n</div>\n			</div> \n			<div id=\"tab-1427368066207-1-3\" class=\"wpb_tab ui-tabs-panel wpb_ui-tabs-hide vc_clearfix\">\n				\n\n		\n			<div class=\"panel entry-content\" id=\"tab-reviews\">\n							</div>\n\n		\n\n			</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n		</div> \n	</div> \n</div><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_no_bg\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-vc-row=\"\"  data-vc=\"4.5.2\"  data-theme-support=\"\"    ></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/petshopper-ecommerce-theme-for-pets-products/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Panthea\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/panthea-multi-purpose-e-commerce-theme/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/panthea-multi-purpose-e-commerce-theme/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 03 Dec 2013 11:49:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://yithemes.com/?post_type=product&p=206155\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:320:\"Panthea is the new YIThemes ecommerce product, a cool, easy to use, customizable and fast WordPress theme designed thinking about users needs and requests. It is a responsive theme and it uses Woo Commerce plugin to set the shop features. With Panthea you can create your completely customized and versatile online shop.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"antoscarface\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21525:\"	<div  class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\n	<div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container \">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n			\n	<div class=\"wpb_tabs wpb_content_element\" data-interval=\"0\">\n		<div class=\"wpb_wrapper wpb_tour_tabs_wrapper ui-tabs vc_clearfix\">\n			<ul class=\"wpb_tabs_nav ui-tabs-nav vc_clearfix\"><li><a href=\"#tab-434e48c3-a84e-7\">Main overview</a></li><li><a href=\"#tab-1427368147528-1-3\">Reviews</a></li></ul>\n\n			\n			<div id=\"tab-434e48c3-a84e-7\" class=\"wpb_tab ui-tabs-panel wpb_ui-tabs-hide vc_clearfix\">\n				\n        <div class=\"row product-features\">\n\n            <div class=\"premium-features col-sm-9\">\n                <h3>Premium Features</h3>\n                <ul class=\"list-inline\">\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Support</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/free-support.png\" alt=\"Support\"/>\n                            <p>We offer a year of support with the purchase of the premium version\r\n, so you can open a new ticket and ask help to our developers. </p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Videotutorial</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/videotutorial.png\" alt=\"Videotutorial\"/>\n                            <p>Setting the theme is easier with our videotutorials, so you can watch how to set each page of the theme step by step.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Sample data</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/sample-data.png\" alt=\"Sample data\"/>\n                            <p>With a simple click you can import our demo files, so your theme will appear exactly like the theme preview.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Extensive Theme Options</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/theme-options.png\" alt=\"Extensive Theme Options\"/>\n                            <p>With our advanced theme options page, you are given complete control over your theme and its settings. </p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>5 slider types</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/slider-type.png\" alt=\"5 slider types\"/>\n                            <p>Compose your page chosing your favourite slider to display your product and images.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Unlimited colors</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/google-font.png\" alt=\"Unlimited colors\"/>\n                            <p>In the premium version of the theme you can easily edit the colors of all the sections and elements like text, links, slogan and so on.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Zoom product image</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/zoom.png\" alt=\"Zoom product image\"/>\n                            <p>You can add a zoom feature in the featured image of products, on the product detail page.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Wishlist</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/wishlist.png\" alt=\"Wishlist\"/>\n                            <p>Give to users the ability to add the products in own withlist.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Compare Products</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/compare.png\" alt=\"Compare Products\"/>\n                            <p>Let your users  compare more products of your shop in one complete table.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Grid and list view</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/grid-list.png\" alt=\"Grid and list view\"/>\n                            <p>In premium version you will be able to choose the layout to display all products in the shop page</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Enquiry form</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/enquiry.png\" alt=\"Enquiry form\"/>\n                            <p>With premium version you can add an enquiry form inside each product detail page.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Custom tabs</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/tabs.png\" alt=\"Custom tabs\"/>\n                            <p>You can add more tabs in the product detail page,   add more features and information  about your products.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Popup</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/popup1.png\" alt=\"Popup\"/>\n                            <p>In premium version you can add a popup to launch your offers and where the users can subscribe in your newsletter list.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Multistep checkout</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/check-multistep.png\" alt=\"Multistep checkout\"/>\n                            <p>With premium version you can have a new checkout layout with a multistep feature.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>600+ google fonts</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/google-font.png\" alt=\"600+ google fonts\"/>\n                            <p>Choose among more than 600 Google fonts to customize typography of your theme as you prefer.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Unlimited contact forms</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/unlimited-contact-form.png\" alt=\"Unlimited contact forms\"/>\n                            <p>Create unlimited contact forms for your site and set up each form very easily by our panel. </p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>4 portfolio layouts</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/portfolio-layout.png\" alt=\"4 portfolio layouts\"/>\n                            <p>Choose your favorite portfolio style and show your projects.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Gallery and videogallery</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/video-galerry.png\" alt=\"Gallery and videogallery\"/>\n                            <p>To show your images and your video projects on your site.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Custom widgets</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/custom-widgets.png\" alt=\"Custom widgets\"/>\n                            <p>Add new and useful widgets in your website pages.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                            <li class=\"col-sm-4\">\n                            <h4>Shortcode manager</h4>\n                            <img src=\"https://yithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/shortcode-manager.png\" alt=\"Shortcode manager\"/>\n                            <p>Through a simple button in the editor bar, you can easily add shortcode in your posts and pages.</p>\n                        </li>\n                                    </ul>\n            </div>\n            <aside class=\"col-sm-3 general-features\">\n\n                <div class=\"quick-info\">\n\n\n                    <h3>Quick info</h3>\n\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled info\">\n                        <li>\n                            <span>version <b>1.4.1</b> - released <b>04-27-2015</b></span>\n                        </li>\n\n                    </ul>\n\n\n                    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"http://docs.yithemes.com/panthea/\"\n                       title=\"View documentation\"\n                       target=\"_blank\">View documentation</a>\n                    <a class=\"btn-sm btn-flat-green\" href=\"#\" title=\"View changelog\"\n                       data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#changelog\">View changelog</a>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"changelog\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-labelledby=\"changelogLabel\"\n                     aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                    <div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n                        <div class=\"modal-content\">\n                            <div class=\"modal-body\">\n                                <button type=\"button\" class=\"close\" data-dismiss=\"modal\" aria-label=\"Close\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">&times;</span></button>\n                                \n\n<h2>Version 1.4.2 - Released: Apr 27, 2015</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Wordpress 4.2 compatibility</li>\n    <li>Added: WooCommerce 2.3.8 support</li>\n    <li>Updated: Revolution Slider to 4.6.9 version</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Wp security issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Version 1.4.1 - Released: Apr 02, 2015</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.3.7</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Ajax Search</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Advanced Reviews</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Order Tracking</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Pdf Invoice</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Cart Message</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Stripe</li>\n	<li>Added: Yith Woocomerce Authorize.net</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Contact Form unsecure issue</li>\n	<li>Fixed: Rich Snippet Compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.4.0 - Released: 02-20-2015</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to WP 4.1.1</li>\n    <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.3.4</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.3.3- Released: 02-04-2015</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to WP 4.1</li>\n	<li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.2.11</li>\n	<li>Updated: Core framework</li>\n	<li>Removed: \"core/yit/Metabox.php\" file</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.3.2- Released: 12-09-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.2.8</li>\n    <li>Added: Linkedin on \"share\" shortcode</li>\n    <li>Added: og:description meta tag</li>\n    <li>Added: Favicon mobile devices option</li>\n    <li>Updated: Revolution Slider 4.6.5</li>\n    <li>Updated: All Around Slider 1.4.5</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Wpml compatibility</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Duplicated Og Meta tags when Seo by Yoast is active</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Image.php issue with W3 Total Cache plugin</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Contact Form lose field value after submit when there are errors</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.3.1 - Released: 10-10-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Woocommerce 2.2.6 support</li>\n    <li>Fixed: \"The settings of this image size have been disabled because its values are being overwritten by a filter.\" because of new WooCommerce 2.2.x</li>\n    <li>Fixed: YIW links problem</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.3.0 - Released: 09-24-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n     <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.2.3</li>\n     <li>Added: Checkout redirect option</li>\n     <li>Added: Filter to change the share text within the loop product. The filter is named yit_other_actions_share_text</li>\n     <li>Added: Filter to change the other actions before send them to page. The filter is named yit_other_actions_args</li>\n     <li>Added: Action attribute on contact form shortcode</li>\n     <li>Added: Show or hide wp admin bar for customers</li>\n     <li>Added: Google Recaptcha System</li>\n     <li>Added: \"Show Breadcrumb\" option on single product page</li>\n     <li>Updated: Revolution Slider 4.6.0</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Incorrect url image on walker menu when user is not logged in</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Google Rich Snippet</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Shipping list layout</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Translation on Tabs title</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Wishlist compatibility</li>\n     <li>Fixed: div minus/plus on ajax navigation filter disappear</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Limited font size in theme options</li>\n     <li>Fixed: og:image dimensions</li>\n     <li>Fixed: \'show_products\' shortcode pagination</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Button icon shortcode</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Panel e Menu Shadow Image</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Firefox and double spinner for number field</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Newsletter email field description</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Widget \"Text Image\" and \"Icon Text\" now suupport text translation</li>\n     <li>Fixed: Contact Forms menu disappear when Contanct Form 7 is installed</li>\n     <li>Removed: tags from wpml-config.xml</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Version 1.2.1 - Released: 03-27-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.1.6</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Responsive widget cart</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Language issues</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Lightbox image navigation</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Style of custom icon \'on sale\'</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Add to cart for grouped product</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Style search box when shop disabled</li>\n    <li>Updated: Revolution slider</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Version 1.2.0 - Released: 03-06-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to Woocommerce 2.1</li>\n    <li>Removed: Wrong option prev/next link from Theme Options</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Option Breadcrumb from Theme Options</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Required checkbox on contact form page</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Version 1.1.0 - Released: 01-07-2014</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>Fixed: Sample data and RevSlider</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Shortcode Category Shift in FF</li>\n    <li>Updated: Revslider 4.1.1</li>\n    <li>Added: support to WP 3.8</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 - Released: 12-03-2013</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial theme version.</li>\n</ul>\n\n	                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                                    <h3>General features</h3>\n\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled general\">\n                                                    <li>\n                                WP 4.0 Compatible                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Responsive design                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                WooCommerce 2.3.X Compatible                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                IE8+, Firefox, Chrome, Opera and Safari Compatible                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Translation ready (.po and .mo files availables)                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Widget ready sidebars                            </li>\n                                                    <li>\n                                Valid XHTML / CSS                            </li>\n                                            